&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;QUALITY OF ACCOMMODATION&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The proposed new dwellinghouse by reason of&amp;nbsp;failing to comply with minimum standards for the gross internal area and&amp;nbsp;minimum width required for a double bedroom (bedroom&amp;nbsp;1)&amp;nbsp;would&amp;nbsp;provide a poor quality of accommodation for current and future occupiers. As such, the proposed development is contrary to the following policies:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;
Policy&amp;nbsp;D6 and Table 3.1 of the London Plan
(March 2021);&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Policies BP5 and BP6&amp;nbsp;of
the&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Borough Wide Development Plan Document (DPD) (March 2011); and&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;
Technical Housing Standards (nationally
described space standard) (DCLG, March 2015) (as amended).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
